Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全世界都疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}World's a crazy place right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟被撕裂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alliances are all torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界破碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The world's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象征的意义来自赋予它们意义的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Symbols are nothing without the women and men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男男女女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that give them meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  美国队长  但这是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Captain America. But this belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我讲讲你最近做的噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me about your most recent nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我知道你经历了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I know that you have been through a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你找回了自己的意志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you've got your mind back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得到了赦免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are being pardoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呦  看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, bam! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他们了吗  他们是你需要担心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see these guys? These are the guys you gotta worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们自称碎旗者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They call themselves Flag Smashers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人想要一个统一无国界的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They want a world that's unified without borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是碎旗者的领导者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, this is the leader of the Flag Smashers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他力气很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  山姆  你快来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God, Sam. You better look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起欢迎新美国队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Join me in welcoming your new Captain America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回顾旧荣光呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reliving the glory days?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得每场比赛前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember sneaking into this locker room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜进这间更衣室来见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before each game to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这或许就是我们稳赢不输的秘诀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's probably why we always won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你紧张吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁  我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做过队长  这当然不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been a captain before, obviously, but this is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都指望我是某个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}expects me to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让他们失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I don't wanna fail them.
