Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-做自己  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Be yourself. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会喜欢你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're gonna love you.
