Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  美国  早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning, America. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  你是美国队长  你不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're Captain America, you're not...
