Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你戏剧课没过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's why you failed drama class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你能相信吗  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you believe this? - I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯  -两周前我们还在组队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - Two weeks ago we're prepping the team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备去智利执行特种任务  现在来干这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for a special ops mission in Chile, now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会  这很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't get me wrong, this has been great,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  但我握了好多手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's been great, but it's been a lot of handshakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多装扮  发表了好多讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a lot of suits, a lot of speeches,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有跟参议员见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and senator meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想好好工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I just wanna do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这就是你的工作  约翰  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is the job, John. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸有成竹的星条旗之子  什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Star-spangled man with a plan and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本就是工作的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always been in the job description.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身衣服  是满载着期待的  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, this suit, it comes with expectations, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后不能靠蛮力解决问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't just punch your way out of problems anymore, you know?
