Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的新美国队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your new Captain America!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning, America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你能来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很开心吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This has gotta be fun, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时过境迁  再回到你的高中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}coming back to your high school after so much has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-约翰·沃克  -真是太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- John Walker! - Oh, it's great. We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  我想大家最想知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}John, I think the first thing everyone wants to know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是做美国队长是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is what is it like being Captain America?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走到哪儿头顶都有老鹰飞过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do eagles fly overhead wherever you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  还有国旗会威武地在空中飘扬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that and flags tend to start majestically waving in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡演如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how's the tour been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他们为你安排了盛大的首秀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know they did a big rollout for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫大荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the greatest honor of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还有些震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, but I'm just a little shocked, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人怎么会走到这一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did a guy like me end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  "我这样的人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, wait, wait, wait. "A guy like me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人太自谦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody's being a bit too humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不了解约翰的简历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For those of you who aren't familiar with his résumé,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}约翰·沃克成为美国队长\N佐治亚州  卡斯特林高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"约翰·沃克  美国历史上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"John Walker, first person in American history
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣获三枚荣誉勋章第一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to receive three Medals of Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾负责绝密反恐任务和人质救援任务"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ran RS-One missions in counterterrorism and hostage rescue."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府在麻省理工学院研究过你的身体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The government did a study of your body at MIT,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在所有可测量门类中都成绩斐然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you tested off the charts in every measurable category.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度  耐力  智力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speed, endurance, intelligence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的  我不是托尼·斯塔克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, here's the thing, uh, I'm not Tony Stark,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是班纳博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not Dr. Banner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有酷炫装备  或超级力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have the flashiest gadgets, I don't have super strength.
