Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是美国队长一直拥有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something Captain America always had,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一直需要的东西  我会需要一切勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}always needs to have, and I'm gonna need every ounce of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我要接过重大的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I got big shoes to fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识史蒂夫·罗杰斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you know Steve Rogers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫回归时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I was two years out of West Point
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已离开西点两年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when Steve came back on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做复仇者时  我一直密切关注他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I followed his career very closely as an Avenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我以他为榜样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like to think that I modeled my work after his.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一直想做个英雄吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you've always wanted to be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴我做的事能给人们安全感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I liked that what I was doing would make people feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫·罗杰斯就是有这种本事的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steve Rogers was the kind of guy who could do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他给了我希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even though I never met him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却觉得他如同我的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he feels like a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}队长回归
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去人不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems like a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}队长回归  约翰·沃克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你见过他吗  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You met him? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你这么急能赶来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for doing this on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我就再检查几件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. No sweat. I'm just finishing up the checklist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到慕尼黑后就一切就绪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be all good to go once you land in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该放弃那盾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't have given up the shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你也很高兴  巴基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good to see you too, Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这不对  -我在工作呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is wrong. - Hey, hey, look, I'm working, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愤怒只能等等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So all this outrage is gonna have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道会发生这种事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't know that was gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然不知道会发生这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, of course I didn't know that was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为看到他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think it didn't break my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推出他来  喊他新美队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to see them march him out there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没伤透我的心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and call him the new Captain America?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫可没想这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't what Steve want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  那你要我怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给美国打电话  告诉他们我改主意了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call America and tell 'em I changed my mind? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  重聚很高兴  兄弟  保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, right. It's a great reunion, buddy, be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无权放弃盾牌  山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had no right to give up the shield, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what you're not gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己的生活都收拾不过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna come here in your overextended life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑来教训我有什么权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and tell me about my rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了  巴基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's over, Bucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  我现在还要处理更严重的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, I have bigger things to deal with now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么比这严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What could be bigger than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟全东欧和中欧的反叛组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His connections with rebel organizations
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有联系  他的力气还非常大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all over Eastern and Central Europe, and he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力气太大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟一个网上组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he's been connected
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎旗者有关联\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to this online group called the Flag Smashers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红翼追踪他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Redwing traced them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到慕尼黑外的一栋建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to a building somewhere outside of Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-所以我要去那里  -我不信任红翼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So that's where I'm going. - Well, I don't trust Redwing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  -你不用信任红翼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hold on a minute. - You don't have to trust Redwing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要去看看他是不是说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'mma go see if he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得他们可能是大三样里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause I have a feeling they might be a part of the Big Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么"大三样"  -大三样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What "Big Three"? - The Big Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么大三样  -人形机器人  外星人  巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What Big Three? - Androids, aliens, and wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-才没这说法  -怎么没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's not a thing. - That's definitely a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我们作战  都是跟这三样中的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every time we fight, it's one of the three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你现在又在跟谁作战  甘道夫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you fighting now, Gandalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道甘道夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know about Gandalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1937年《霍比特人》刚出版时我就读过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I read The Hobbit in 1937 when it first came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-所以你明白我的意思了吧  -我不  巫师不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So you see my point? - No, I don't. There are no wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-奇异博士  -是个法师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Doctor Strange. - Is a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师就是不戴巫师帽的巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A sorcerer is a wizard without a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想吧  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think about it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是对的  我才想出来的  多疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm right. I just came up with that. It's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不是重点  这些人没魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But look, that's not the point. These guys aren't magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们跟你一样用蛮力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. They use brute force like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我面前这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the incredibly annoying guy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱瞪眼的烦人家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in front of me with the staring problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我跟你一起去  -别做梦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm coming with you. - No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}德国  慕尼黑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一分钟下机  山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One minute to drop off, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么打算的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what's our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  没打算咯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great. So no plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-旅途愉快  巴基  -不  你不能那么喊我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Enjoy your ride, Buck. - No, you can't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  史蒂夫就那么喊你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not? That's what Steve called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫认识我更久  而且他总有计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steve knew me longer, and Steve had a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15秒离机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fifteen seconds to drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落伞呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the chute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是60米  太低空不能跳伞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're at 200 feet, man. It's too low for a chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反正也不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全拍下来了  你知道吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have all of that on camera. You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚远点  山姆  不然我揍暴它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of my face, Sam, or I'll break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  往北来  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, head north. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在瞪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're doing the staring thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那人呢  -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's the guy? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们好像在偷运军火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think they're smuggling weapons, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能想对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I think you could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要一探究竟只有一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看这条路很通畅  我们上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see a clear path. I say we take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是刺客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们里面见  随你便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you inside or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  伙计  我闹你呢  回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, come on, man. I'm just messing with you. Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你  蹑手蹑脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at you. All stealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瓦坎达待了一阵  就变成白豹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A little time in Wakanda and you come out White Panther.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's actually White Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我进来了  所以我比你领先好多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I'm inside. Therefore, way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是特别理想  但很可行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not great, but very doable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  我错过了什么  什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. What did I miss? Nothing.
