Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没想到盾牌会落到我手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't think that the shield was gonna end up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂  巴基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it, Bucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我不是想成为史蒂夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm... I'm not trying to be Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想替代史蒂夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not trying to replace Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想成为我能成为的最优秀的美国队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just trying to be the best Captain America I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果队长的左膀右臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'd be a whole lot easier
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在我身边  就会简单得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I had Cap's wingmen on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是最后一句话坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always that last line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们肯定快要饿死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be famished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-饿极了  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Very hungry. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-对  我们饿了  -好  我妻子和我做了饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, we are hungry. - Okay. My wife and I cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是按我家祖传秘方做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an old family recipe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用的是最好的鸡肝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}made with the finest chicken livers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please serve yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要什么都可以  什么都行  尽管告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you want. Anything. You ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有咖啡  还有些饼干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is some coffee here and some crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这些够了  谢谢  -为了大业  我们愿做一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're okay. Thank you. - Uh, anything we can do for the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.22,0:23:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都快成为传奇人物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're becoming a bit of a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到越来越多的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear more and more people talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起你们这些反抗的自由斗士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the freedom fighters who are pushing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫你们侠盗罗宾汉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They call you Robin Hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都有越来越多的人喜爱你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every day more people love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所到之处  都会有人给予庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll find refuge wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:24:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我妻子专为你们布置的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My wife and I made this just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都非常干净\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything is completely clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不错  -她布置得温馨舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - She made it really nice and cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢你  -别客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天  能睡床了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my gosh, beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}未知联系人  匿名号码\N你夺走了我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}我会找到你  杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种食物最适合你了  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This has your name written all over it, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们住得舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hope you feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bis morgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.27,0:24:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  他们已经在通缉我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit. They're already looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.21,0:24:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把我们的化名从所有公共交通网站上抹去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm wiping our aliases off any public traffic sites now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}国际刑警组织通缉令
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.74,0:24:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉  我们不能在这里久留\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karli, we can't stay here for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.62,0:24:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}通缉  卡莉·摩根索  最后出现在慕尼黑附近\N持有武器  请格外谨慎应对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.94,0:24:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六个月前  你们能想象到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months ago would you have imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有这么多人支持我们的大业吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}people supporting the cause like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不再小打小闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not playing no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.41,0:24:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能让那些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't let these same assholes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在"闪烁"后重新掌权的混蛋赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who were put back in power after The Blip win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球回归委员会更在乎那些回归者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The GRC care more about the people who came back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是那些从未消失的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than the ones who never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.41,0:24:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经窥见了更好的可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a glimpse of how things could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.10,0:24:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要确定你们都是真心参与的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know that you're all committed,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.37,0:24:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为明天之后  就再不能回头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because after tomorrow, there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.09,0:25:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  同一世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. One world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.21,0:25:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.93,0:25:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-同一世界  -同一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- One world. - One people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.78,0:25:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-同一世界  -同一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- One world! - One people!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.45,0:25:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.58,0:25:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山姆  我们去把盾牌拿走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's take the shield, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.65,0:25:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走盾牌  然后我们单干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's take the shield and do this ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.49,0:25:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能就这么冲到他面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't just run up on the man,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他揍一顿  然后拿走盾牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beat him up, and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.65,0:25:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我们上次偷盾牌之后发生的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember what happened the last time we stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.58,0:25:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-也许吧  -以防万一  我提醒你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe. - I'll help you in case you forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.60,0:25:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎伦被列为国家公敌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sharon was branded enemy of the state,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.65,0:25:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫和我逃亡了整整两年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Steve and I were on the run for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你怎么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.78,0:25:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反正不想下半辈子都颠沛流离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I don't wanna live the rest of my life la vida loca.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.58,0:25:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚被那些超级士兵暴揍一通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just got our ass handed to us by Super Soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.04,0:25:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.56,0:26:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不完全是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.93,0:26:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个人你应该去见见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is someone that you should meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.95,0:26:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}马里兰州  巴尔的摩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.34,0:26:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是黑猎鹰  你好  -孩子  就叫猎鹰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's Black Falcon. What's up? - It's just Falcon, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.49,0:26:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不对  我爸告诉我你是黑猎鹰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. My daddy told me it's Black Falcon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.11,0:26:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我是黑人也是猎鹰吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it because I'm black and I'm the Falcon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.55,0:26:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格地说  是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, technically, I mean, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.49,0:26:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是什么  黑孩子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So are you, like, Black kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.62,0:26:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他无话可说了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.28,0:26:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.05,0:27:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.40,0:27:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.28,0:27:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.79,0:27:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来见以赛亚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're here to see Isaiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.58,0:27:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有什么以赛亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody named Isaiah live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.74,0:27:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想和他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we just want to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.62,0:27:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听见我刚才说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must not hear what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.11,0:27:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ain't getting in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.36,0:27:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们赶紧走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Y'all can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.43,0:27:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他  高阳酒吧的那个人来见他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him the guy from the bar in Goyang is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.34,0:27:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会明白我什么意思的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gonna know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.90,0:27:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  在这儿等着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.04,0:27:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子挺好  你怎么认识这个人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice kid. How do you know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.68,0:27:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.75,0:28:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在朝鲜战争时我们有过一次小摩擦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had a skirmish during the Korean War.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.21,0:28:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们今天运气不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他要亲自见你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he wanna see for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.54,0:28:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以赛亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isaiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.76,0:28:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是山姆  山姆  这是以赛亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is, uh, Sam. Sam, this is Isaiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.14,0:28:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一位英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九头蛇最惧怕的人之一  就像史蒂夫一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the ones that HYDRA feared the most. Like Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.50,0:28:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是1951年认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We met in '51.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.04,0:28:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说的"认识"是指我把你揍翻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If by met, you mean I whupped your ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.99,0:28:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.02,0:28:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得到密报说他在朝鲜半岛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We heard whispers he was on the peninsula,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是所有被派去抓他的人都有去无回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but everyone they sent after him, never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.35,0:28:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美国军方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the U.S. Military dropped me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.49,0:28:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我深入敌后去对付他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}behind the line to go deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.47,0:28:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阳那次打斗中  我扯下了他半条金属手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took half that metal arm in that fight in Goyang,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.15,0:29:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我看他又想办法长回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I see he's managed to grow it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.48,0:29:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们进来  我就想看看他手臂恢复没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to see if he got the arm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.03,0:29:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者他是不是来杀我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or if he'd come to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.13,0:29:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不再是杀手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a killer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.47,0:29:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你能某天醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you can wake up one day
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定自己想成为什么人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and decide who you wanna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.74,0:29:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.79,0:29:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你这样的人是可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe it does for folks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.03,0:29:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以赛亚  我们来这里是因为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isaiah, the reason we're here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.54,0:29:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了更多你我这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is because there's more of you and me out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.65,0:29:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你我这样的人  -我们要知道是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You and me. - And we need to know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.93,0:29:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再谈这件事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna talk about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.12,0:29:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们是怎么对待我这个英雄的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what they did to me for being a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.91,0:30:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把我关进监狱30年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They put my ass in jail for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.62,0:30:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断有人给我做检测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People running tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.76,0:30:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽我的血  进入我的牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}taking my blood, coming into my cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.13,0:30:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连你的同类也不放过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even your people weren't done with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.76,0:30:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-以赛亚  -从我家里滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Isaiah... - Get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.35,0:30:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  出去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go, man, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.66,0:30:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-山姆  -你为什么没跟我说起过以赛亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sam... - Why didn't you tell me about Isaiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.91,0:30:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么从来都没人提起过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could nobody bring him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.10,0:30:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我问你话呢  巴基  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I asked you a question, Bucky. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.92,0:30:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫也不知道他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steve didn't know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.97,0:30:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我没跟他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't. I didn't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.41,0:30:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你是说  几十年前有个黑人超级战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're telling me that there was a black Super Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.19,0:30:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却没人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}decades ago and nobody knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.60,0:30:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  两位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有什么问题吗  -没  我们聊天呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is there a problem here? - No, we're just talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.70,0:30:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.05,0:30:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看看你的证件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I see your ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.57,0:30:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我没有证件  怎么了  -没搞错吧你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't have ID. Why? - Man, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.66,0:30:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  冷静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, sir, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.93,0:31:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冷静  你们想干什么  我们只是站着聊天而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am calm. What do you want? We're just standing and talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.29,0:31:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把你的证件给他  我们就能走了  -我他妈才不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Give him your ID so we can leave. - No. I'm not giving him shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.80,0:31:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们只是在聊天  -他缠着你不放吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're just talking. - Is he bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.29,0:31:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有缠着我不放  你知道他是谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, he's not bothering me. Do you know who this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.99,0:31:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位是复仇者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These guys are Avengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  实在是对不起  威尔逊先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God, I am so sorry, Mr. Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.29,0:31:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没戴护目镜我都认不出您了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't recognize you without the goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.97,0:31:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm really, really sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位先在这等一下好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guys, just wait here, okay? Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟任何人说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't... I didn't tell anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.09,0:31:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他已经受了太多苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he had already been through enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.95,0:31:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴恩斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Barnes,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.43,0:31:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有一张你的逮捕令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a warrant out for your arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.39,0:31:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统都已经赦免他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, the president pardoned him for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.61,0:31:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是因为你没去法庭强制的心理治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for that. You missed your court-mandated therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.39,0:31:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没在规定的时间跟假释官报到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like missing a check-in with your PO.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.94,0:31:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  巴纳斯先生  你被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Mr. Barnes, you're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.63,0:32:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山姆  久仰大名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam. I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.64,0:32:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是雷纳医生  詹姆斯的心理医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Dr. Raynor. I'm James's therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.69,0:32:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会  感谢你捞他出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So nice to meet you. Thank you for getting him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.21,0:32:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.40,0:32:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.42,0:32:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴再次见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's great to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.90,0:32:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧  你认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta be kidding me. You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.70,0:32:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我们以前一起出过外勤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we did some field ops back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.90,0:32:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你在给巴基做心理治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard you were working with Bucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.73,0:32:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得我该出手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I thought I'd step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.27,0:32:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基不需要再严格按时去见你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bucky's not gonna be following a strict schedule any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.08,0:32:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗还没结束呢  谁批准的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We haven't finished our work. Who authorized this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.00,0:33:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这样的人才不应该被束缚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's too valuable of an asset to have tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.10,0:33:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就给他治疗完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just do whatever you got to do with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.34,0:33:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把他交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then send him off to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.31,0:33:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他还有事没解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got some unfinished business, him and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.10,0:33:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  威尔逊  我在外面等你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You too, Wilson. I'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.16,0:33:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯  放了你的条件是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}James, condition of your release,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.73,0:33:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始心理咨询  你也一样  山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}session now. You too, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.12,0:33:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我会在外面和...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's okay. I'll be out here with...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.40,0:33:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在和你商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.51,0:33:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.55,0:33:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁想先说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who would like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.07,0:33:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  雷纳医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, look, Dr. Raynor?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.27,0:33:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你为什么想让我和这位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it, why you want me to talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.81,0:33:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常脱线的怪人谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freaky Magoo over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.40,0:33:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心理非常健康\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm 100% fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.35,0:33:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的职责就是确认你真的没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is my job to make sure that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.81,0:33:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  虽然有点不专业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so, yeah, this may be slightly unprofessional,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.32,0:33:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有通过这一方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's the only way that I can see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.72,0:33:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能知道你是否能克服内心恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you're getting over whatever's eating at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.36,0:34:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这太扯了  -我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is ridiculous. - Yeah. I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.75,0:34:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗  已经有进展了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See? Making progress already.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.75,0:34:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  谁想先来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, who wants to go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.42,0:34:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人主动来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No volunteers?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. How surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.53,0:34:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们现在做个练习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. We're going to do an exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.30,0:34:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当有夫妻想搞清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's something I use with couples
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.63,0:34:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想共同构建怎样的生活时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they are trying to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.60,0:34:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会用这个练习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what kind of life they wanna build together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.91,0:34:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听说过奇迹问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you familiar with the miracle question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.65,0:34:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-闻所未闻  -见所未见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Absolutely not. - Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.99,0:34:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个练习是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, it goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设在你睡觉的时候出现了一个奇迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suppose that while you're sleeping, a miracle occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.60,0:34:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒来之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.88,0:34:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what is something that you would like to see
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.22,0:34:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让你的生活变好的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that would make your life better?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.06,0:34:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的奇迹就是  他能少说点话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my miracle, he would... he would talk less.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.51,0:34:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我想说的一模一样  真够讽刺的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly what I was gonna say. Isn't that ironic?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.16,0:34:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们俩逼我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You guys are leaving me with no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.28,0:34:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在该进行灵魂凝视练习了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time for the soul-gazing exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.06,0:34:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我更喜欢这个  -天哪  他肯定会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I like this better. - Oh, God. He's gonna love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.97,0:34:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我准备好了  -这正合你的口味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, I'm ready. - This is right up your alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.79,0:34:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过来  面对彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turn around. Face each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.55,0:34:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定会乐在其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should really enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.97,0:34:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.82,0:34:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.28,0:35:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山姆  面对面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam. Face each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.24,0:35:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  试试灵魂凝视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's do it. Let's stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-靠近点  -这个练习真不错  谢谢你医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get close. -This is a good exercise. Thanks, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.33,0:35:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  再靠近点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, good. All right, get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.96,0:35:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近一点点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.39,0:35:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腿想放哪边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which way you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.55,0:35:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-右还是左  -你的腿怎么是张开的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right or left? - Why're your legs open?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.58,0:35:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样  你满意了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? Fine. Here. You happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.74,0:35:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-行了  -就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.62,0:35:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很好  -我们动不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good. Fine. - We're locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.93,0:35:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有点近了  -是非常近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's a little close. - That's very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.30,0:35:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正合你意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.18,0:35:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.89,0:35:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  现在看着彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Now look at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.64,0:35:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要看着对方的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to look at each other in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.10,0:35:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  也没有那么难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There, you see? That wasn't so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.01,0:35:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你们在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.00,0:35:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩在瞪眼比赛吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you having a staring contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.97,0:35:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眨眨眼  上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just blink. Sweet Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.83,0:35:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  詹姆斯  山姆哪里惹到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, James, why does Sam aggravate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:35:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说幼稚的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't say something childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.82,0:36:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么放弃了盾牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you give up that shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.06,0:36:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么在意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you making such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.67,0:36:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件跟你没有任何关系的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}out of something that has nothing to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.05,0:36:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂夫相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steve believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.27,0:36:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.01,0:36:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把盾给你是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He gave you that shield for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.95,0:36:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块盾  那是他守护的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That shield, that is... that is everything he stood for.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.94,0:36:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的传承\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is his legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.93,0:36:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把盾给了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He gave you that shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.96,0:36:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却根本不当一回事  直接扔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you threw it away like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.90,0:36:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-闭嘴  -也许他是看错你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shut up. - So maybe he was wrong about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.37,0:36:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他看错了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if he was wrong about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.37,0:36:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他也看错了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then he was wrong about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.07,0:36:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.35,0:36:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.27,0:36:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你和史蒂夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe this is something you or Steve
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.75,0:36:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不可能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.19,0:36:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你能不能接受  我做了我认为正确的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But can you accept that I did what I thought was right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.88,0:36:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生  我不想再这样浪费时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what, Doc? I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.83,0:37:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有很重要的事要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have some real serious shit going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.65,0:37:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.18,0:37:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我再也不纠结了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will squash it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.44,0:37:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们办完那件事以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go deal with that, and when we're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.20,0:37:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就分道扬镳  享受一段漫长的假期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we both can go on separate, long vacations
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.03,0:37:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不相见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.05,0:37:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这主意不错  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I like that. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.72,0:37:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生  谢谢你弄了这一出尴尬事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Doc, for making it weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.38,0:37:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉可是好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.47,0:37:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.98,0:37:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你才是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.58,0:37:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.07,0:37:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熟悉这个表情  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that look. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.07,0:37:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二条规则是什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was rule number two again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.17,0:37:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许让任何人受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.03,0:37:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.44,0:37:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.12,0:37:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得糟透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.34,0:38:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次见到你们真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.20,0:38:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们搞分裂  就只会失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, if we divide ourselves, we don't stand a chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.78,0:38:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都很清楚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you guys know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.14,0:38:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what do you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.05,0:38:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的领导者名叫卡莉·摩根索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the leader's name's Karli Morgenthau.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.87,0:38:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在追查那些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been targeting civilians
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.98,0:38:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助卡莉四处流窜的平民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who've been helping Karli move from place to place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.38,0:38:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们标记一个地点  然后干扰信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They geotagged a location, then scrambled the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.35,0:38:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们的卫星在欧洲中部和东部的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But our satellites have found their symbol popping up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.67,0:38:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多个回归安置社区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in various displaced communities
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.41,0:38:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了他们的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all across Central and Eastern Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.73,0:38:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得她把刚偷的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think that she's taking the medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.07,0:38:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带到了其中一个营地里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she just stole to one of these camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.84,0:38:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"闪烁"之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there are hundreds of those
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.27,0:38:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球冒出了几百个这种营地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all over the planet since The Blip.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.04,0:38:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们得费大功夫好好找了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I guess you'll have to look real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.09,0:38:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我的视力特别棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good thing I have 20/20 vision, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.13,0:38:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在在哪里  沃克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she now, Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.21,0:38:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道吗  -我们不知道  巴基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you know? - No, we don't know, Bucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.19,0:38:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们迟早会找到她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only a matter of time before we find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.34,0:38:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定很吃力吧  沃克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things are really intense for you, aren't they, Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.67,0:38:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点  沃克说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it easy. Look, Walker's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.38,0:38:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须找到他们  并阻止他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is imperative that we find them and stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.29,0:38:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们有干涉限制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you guys have rules of engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.27,0:39:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要申请各种授权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and all kind of authorizations you have to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.14,0:39:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是自由人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're free agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.32,0:39:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们更灵活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're more flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.42,0:39:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也不该和你们一起行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it wouldn't make sense for us to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.20,0:39:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给你们一个建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A word of advice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.64,0:39:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来碍我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay the hell out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}斯洛伐克  布拉迪斯拉发
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.57,0:39:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  我们得赶紧转移了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it! We gotta move out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.25,0:39:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们找到我们了  -我们还有多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They found us. - How much time do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.29,0:39:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  是权力掮客的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None. It's The Power Broker's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.49,0:39:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人能拿多少拿多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody, grab what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.65,0:39:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能给你争取时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can give you time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.18,0:39:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拖住他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.71,0:39:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.66,0:40:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一世界  同一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One world. One people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.91,0:40:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.40,0:40:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.50,0:40:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  不许动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}stop right there. Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.45,0:40:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪  打他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hit him, open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.21,0:41:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.91,0:41:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我们要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know what we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.00,0:41:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以赛亚说"我的同类"时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When Isaiah said "My people"...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.64,0:41:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别往心里去  他不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, don't take that to heart. That's not what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.84,0:41:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他说的是九头蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, he meant HYDRA.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.48,0:41:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前  九头蛇才是我的同类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}HYDRA used to be my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.31,0:41:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克毫无头绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Walker doesn't have any leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.41,0:41:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想干什么  不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know where you're going with this, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.94,0:41:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道九头蛇所有秘密  你忘了西伯利亚的事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows all of HYDRA's secrets. Don't you remember Siberia?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.47,0:41:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就打算和那家伙坐下来好好聊聊吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're just gonna go sit in a room with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.34,0:41:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.53,0:42:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.37,0:42:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去见泽莫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna go see Zemo.

